Notes: Wheaton wins its seventh-straight by upsetting 10th-ranked Illinois Wesleyan.
Wheaton gains sole posession of first place in the CCIW at 10-1.
Wheaton will travel to second-place Millikin on Tuesday in a key CCIW game.
